The paper uses deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (AI), and hence cs.AI is another likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the performance of the attack framework, which falls under the category of Machine Learning (ML), and hence cs.LG (Learning) is another likely sub-category.
